<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.6">
<l>tōṟṟak kēṭavai yilla vaṉṉuṭai yāṉa vaṉoru mūrttiyāyc</l>
<l>cīṟṟat tōṭaruḷ peṟṟa vaṉaṭik kīḻppu kaniṉṟa ceṅkaṇmā</l>
<l>ṉāṟṟan tōṟṟañ cuvaiyo liyuṟa lāki niṉṟavem vāṉava</l>
<l>rēṟṟai yēyaṉṟi maṟṟo ruvarai yāṉi lēṉeḻu maikkumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one without these: appearance [and] disappearance, the master, red-eyed Māl</l>
<l>who stood while the one who obtained [his] grace with anger entered below [his] feet, being his one form,</l>
<l>our bull of the celestials who stood as smell, appearance, taste, sound [and] touch,</l>
<l>apart from him I am without any other through seven births.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
